<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Thorncliffe</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">One of Calgary’s prime residential neighborhoods, Thorncliffe is bound by the Nose Hill Park on the west, the McKnight Boulevard on the south, the Deerfoot Trail on the east and the 64 Avenue on the north. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">With its beautiful tree-lined streets, clean walking trails, gentle rolling hill slopes and sprawling green spaces, the community in Thorncliffe is a true paradise for raising your kids and relishing your tranquil life post-retirement. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">With a myriad of shopping malls and recreational venues located at a stone’s throw from most of the residential units, life in Thorncliffe is both convenient and enjoyable.</p>
        </div>
